{"tid":2131031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"01記者問政府海員邊個決定 政務司話運房局提出 運房局話係政務局拍板","createTime":"2020-07-29T14:23:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T15:41:46.000Z","uid":22556,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6bf8115854a4ab9dadd7e9ef094395a7223a2cbe","tid":2131031,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:23:22.000Z","msg":"負責推動豁免船員檢疫的運輸及房屋局，在回應《香港01》查詢時透露更多資料，包括局長陳帆曾與香港船東會及香港定期班輪協會代表，於今年5月見面討論。<br />\n而運房局與最終拍板的政務司司長辦公室，均指食衛局在推出措施前，已評估豁免風險。<br />\n<br />\n負責「拍板」豁免安排的政務司司長辦公室，透過政府新聞處回覆，確認海員豁免安排由運輸及房屋局提出，而食物及衞生局就負責作公共衞生風險評估，然後向政務司司長作出建議。<br />\n<br />\n01唔貼Link"},{"pid":"97754feee6e5661ce35177aa52dacead62903223","tid":2131031,"uid":35661,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"今次我真係愛莫能助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166ce3d0dd2bd8910925ebdbc16f2acb4b033e50","tid":2131031,"uid":58958,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:25:44.000Z","msg":"射齊未？"},{"pid":"45c9c3b629d781e68294fb518199bedfe0427ae1","tid":2131031,"uid":146285,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:26:13.000Z","msg":"職場卸膊操<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f107b466afa9c03c98adf5336ed935463ff8120b","tid":2131031,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"45c9c3b629d781e68294fb518199bedfe0427ae1","tid":2131031,"uid":146285,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:26:13.000Z","msg":"職場卸膊操<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:27:24.000Z","msg":"呢次我真係幫你唔到.gif"},{"pid":"a389137b47bb4e1eb3bdaecf723cfb4bab40bc17","tid":2131031,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:38:55.000Z","msg":"明明就係柒婆拍板，結果個波就推